title: Murder Hamster Economics
author: VD
content_html:
After all, we have been informed that it cannot possibly be GENETIC factors that contribute to a propensity toward violence. Although I suppose E. Michael Jones would insist it was the absence of a proper Catholic culture and upbringing that is responsible, not economic deprivement.
